The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Simarjeet favourite

A STAFF REPORTER

Calcutta: Three-time Sri Lankan Open winner Simarjeet Singh will be the top rated player to take part in the Royal Challenge RCGC Cup ? starting on Tuesday ? to be followed by the Eastern India Amateur Golf Championship. The RCGC Cup will be a four-day affair, while the amateur meet will be held from December 19-25. 

The Eastern India meet, ? which will attract nearly 100 participants ? will be played in two formats ? strokeplay and matchplay, while the RCGC Cup will be played in the strokeplay format for over four days. 




